predictions.article: Trade war escalates as retaliatory tariffs hit struggling farm economy
predictions.prediction: U.S. agricultural exports to China, Canada, and Mexico will decrease by at least 10% within the next month due to the newly imposed tariffs.

predictions.article: China Hits U.S. Agriculture, Says It Won't Be Bullied by Fresh Trump Tariffs
predictions.prediction: Prices for U.S. soybeans and corn will decrease by at least 5% within the next month as a result of China's retaliatory tariffs.
